OL,6,FA former headteacher has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of sexually abusing four girls
OL,8,Fover a four-year period.
OL,10,FNeil Foden, 66, of Old Colwyn was
OL,11,Ffound guilty of 19 charges, including
OL,12,F12 of sexual activity with a child.
