OL,6,FHe was found not guilty of one charge
OL,7,Fof sexual activity with a child. After
OL,8,Fjust over a day of deliberation, the
OL,9,Fjury returned their verdict on
OL,10,FWednesday, 15 May, after an almost
OL,11,Ffour-week trial.
OL,13,FFoden, who had denied all the charges,
OL,14,Fstared ahead as the verdicts were read
OL,15,Fout and showed no emotion.
OL,17,FHe is due to be sentenced at Mold
OL,18,FCrown Court on Monday, 1 July.
