OL,6,FJudge Rhys Rowlands warned he would go
OL,7,Fto jail and would receive a lengthy
OL,8,Fsentence.
OL,10,FThe judge told Foden "some of the
OL,11,Fexplanations for your behaviour
OL,12,Ftowards the victims proffered by you
OL,13,Fbeggared belief at times".
OL,15,FHe said he had shown himself to be
OL,16,F"arrogant" with a "controlling
OL,17,Fpersonality" and an "individual used
OL,18,Fto getting his own way".
