OL,6,FHe added: "This defendant was arrogant
OL,7,Fand couldn't care less. He was Neil
OL,8,FFoden, a man in his view who could do
OL,9,Fno wrong."
OL,11,FJudge Rowlands criticised Cyngor
OL,12,FGwynedd (Gwynedd Council) for not
OL,13,Finvestigating concerns about Foden
OL,14,Fmeeting girls alone as far back as
OL,15,F2019.
OL,17,FHe said: "It does appear to me that
OL,18,Fwhen real concerns were raised with
OL,19,Fthe council in 2019 they were
OL,20,Fdismissed.
