OL,6,F"Now that the criminal process has
OL,7,Fconcluded, the task of reviewing work
OL,8,Fpractices and establishing what
OL,9,Flessons can be learnt will begin. Due
OL,10,Fto the serious nature of the case,
OL,11,Farrangements are being made to carry
OL,12,Fout an independent review in
OL,13,Faccordance with national Child
OL,14,FPractice Review guidelines. The exact
OL,15,Fform of the review is currently being
OL,16,Fdetermined.
OL,18,F"Until all relevant investigations and
OL,19,Freviews have been completed, it would
OL,20,Fnot be appropriate to comment further."
