OL,6,FChildren's Commissioner for Wales
OL,7,FRocio Cifuentes said: "The actions
OL,8,Fsurrounding these offences and how
OL,9,Fconcerns were dealt with must now be
OL,10,Ffully investigated.
OL,12,F"I contacted the local authority for
OL,13,Fassurances as soon as I was made aware
OL,14,Fof Mr Foden's arrest in connection
OL,15,Fwith these offences. I'll be meeting
OL,16,Fwith senior officials from the
OL,17,Fauthority in the next few weeks to
OL,18,Festablish what steps they'll be taking
OL,19,Fto learn from this.
