OL,6,F"Professionals working with children
OL,7,Fhave a duty to report any concerns
OL,8,Fabout suspected risk of abuse, and
OL,9,Fchildren who come forward must be
OL,10,Flistened to and taken seriously. If
OL,11,Fanyone is unsure about whether or
OL,12,Fwhere to take any concerns forward
OL,13,Fthey can contact my office or the
OL,14,FNSPCC."
OL,16,FFoden had also been a teaching union
OL,17,Fleader and a local spokesman on
